# write-stories — user stories

## When to invoke

The user wants classic user stories with acceptance criteria (Card / Conversation / Confirmation style).

## Steps

1. Capture the persona, need, and benefit (“As a … I want … so that …”).
2. Add **Acceptance criteria** as bullet checks a reviewer can verify.
3. Note dependencies, data, and non-goals if relevant.
4. Save items where the team tracks backlog (e.g. planning doc or issue links).
